I think it's ironic that with all the effort, money, and threats that
have been put into keeping crypto technology within our borders, our
own patent system keeps the best, most inexpensive out of the hands of
Americans and squarely in the hands of all those we'd try and keep it
from.

"Strange and wonderful times..."

